,"location":2,"to":271.18},{"content":"兄弟齐心 奋发努力才行啊","from":271.52,"location":2,"to":275.23},{"content":"真是烦人的虫子","from":280.37,"location":2,"to":282.45},{"content":"这么说","from":283.29,"location":2,"to":284.26},{"content":"清盛那厮已经魂不守舍了？","from":284.44,"location":2,"to":287.84},{"content":"是","from":288.02,"location":2,"to":288.38},{"content":"(藤原基房：殿下争道事件当事人。此时已卸任摄政，转任关白。)","from":288.38,"location":2,"to":289.15},{"content":"已经成了一个寻常的痴呆老头啊\n(藤原基房：殿下争道事件当事人。此时已卸任摄政，转任关白。)","from":289.15,"location":2,"to":292.31},{"content":"这真乃天赐良机","from":294.03,"location":2,"to":296.97},{"content":"你说后白河法皇？","from":312.08,"location":2,"to":313.92},{"content":"是","from":314.23,"location":2,"to":315.01},{"content":"他没收了重盛长子维盛继承的越前领地…\n(越前国：在琵琶湖之北，面向日本海，今福井县及石川县一带。)","from":315.4,"location":2,"to":320.5},{"content":"此前盛子掌管的藤原家家产 也遭没收了","from":322.49,"location":2,"to":328.78},{"content":"这段时间","from":331.21,"location":2,"to":332.53},{"content":"他又对朝廷的人事安排颇多置喙","from":332.72,"location":2,"to":337.1},{"content":"这混账","from":337.88,"location":2,"to":339.26},{"content":"父亲？","from":340.75,"location":2,"to":341.93},{"content":"竟敢自行其是","from":342.43,"location":2,"to":345.1},{"content":"父亲！","from":345.66,"location":2,"to":346.72},{"content":"父亲…","from":347.89,"location":2,"to":348.75},{"content":"父亲…","from":350.08,"location":2,"to":351.52},{"content":"宗盛 出兵","from":354.03,"location":2,"to":355.84},{"content":"为父也要回京","from":357.59,"location":2,"to":359.15},{"content":"为父还没老呢！","from":361.23,"location":2,"to":363.49},{"content":"速速让道 速速让道","from":371.56,"location":2,"to":373.59},{"content":"是清盛大人","from":373.59,"location":2,"to":374.62},{"content":"他是要报复朝廷啊","from":374.62,"location":2,"to":376.62},{"content":"父亲 您可算回来了","from":381.27,"location":2,"to":383.69},{"content":"宗盛","from":388.93,"location":2,"to":389.64},{"content":"在","from":389.64,"location":2,"to":390.18},{"content":"知盛","from":390.5,"location":2,"to":391.2},{"content":"在","from":391.2,"location":2,"to":391.76},{"content":"重衡","from":391.86,"location":2,"to":392.61},{"content":"在","from":392.61,"location":2,"to":393.17},{"content":"即日起","from":394.4,"location":2,"to":395.43},{"content":"将摄政关白及以下的四十三人解职","from":395.72,"location":2,"to":400.04},{"content":"今后 皆由我平家族人担任","from":401.04,"location":2,"to":404.42},{"content":"特别是收取重盛领地的关白基房","from":405.18,"location":2,"to":409.03},{"content":"将那厮流放日向国\n(日向国：在今九州岛西南。)","from":409.68,"location":2,"to":412.4},{"content":"出阵了 快走 快走！","from":413.14,"location":2,"to":415.74},{"content":"-速速开门 -从那包抄","from":419.72,"location":2,"to":421.67},{"content":"-全都抓起来！ -休要抵抗！","from":421.8,"location":2,"to":424.15},{"content":"-别放跑了！ -饶命啊！","from":424.15,"location":2,"to":426.0},{"content":"臣已出家 还望免去流放日向之刑啊","from":426.41,"location":2,"to":430.89},{"content":"既如此 就改为流放备前吧","from":431.46,"location":2,"to":435.13},{"content":"宗盛","from":435.62,"location":2,"to":436.42},{"content":"在","from":436.42,"location":2,"to":436.92},{"content":"你去见法皇陛下 请他移居鸟羽离宫","from":437.11,"location":2,"to":443.07},{"content":"您要幽禁法皇陛下？","from":443.86,"location":2,"to":445.6},{"content":"若真把事做绝…","from":445.6,"location":2,"to":447.11},{"content":"是！孩儿这就去办！","from":447.92,"location":2,"to":450.19},{"content":"连我也要？","from":454.56,"location":2,"to":456.28},{"content":"平家武士竟敢反噬我等主君！","from":458.6,"location":2,"to":462.81},{"content":"绝不饶你 绝不饶你 清盛！","from":466.33,"location":2,"to":470.44},{"content":"八尺镜 天丛云剑 八尺琼勾玉","from":490.14,"location":2,"to":495.43},{"content":"此三神器 乃是天子之证","from":495.68,"location":2,"to":500.24},{"content":"你可是历代天子中 继位时最年少的","from":500.52,"location":2,"to":504.41},{"content":"这不是年少 而是太过幼小吧","from":504.58,"location":2,"to":506.89},{"content":"德子 你应该更高兴些才是啊","from":507.31,"location":2,"to":509.9},{"content":"你的儿子 我的外孙当天皇了","from":510.25,"location":2,"to":514.33},{"content":"对不对？","from":514.44,"location":2,"to":515.16},{"content":"你看 他也知道这是喜事","from":517.75,"location":2,"to":520.52},{"content":"另外…","from":521.98,"location":2,"to":523.08},{"content":"高仓上皇陛下","from":525.0